"replyTime":"2017-09-29T06:43:23.000Z","msg":"化學味好重"},{"pid":"5145e2aa8dc9faff00ff052598f95867729bc3aa","tid":416080,"uid":50347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T06:45:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/28/122627_423942f3cd6559ae3ebb717209447e11.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F28%2F122627_423942f3cd6559ae3ebb717209447e11.jpg&h=9df24cb4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nlunch即刻去屌返支<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82091e44b75bf86d30da2005eb5826dd03b5f2ec","tid":416080,"uid":143210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T08:29:31.000Z","msg":"椰奶蜜瓜奶大愛jj<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61ce931e7242ca6921a10fb19d7d7189494a6516","tid":416080,"uid":51387,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T08:59:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>柑香茶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n早排第一次飲，竟然幾好味</blockquote><br />\n我寧願飲橙汁，浸味怪到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n柑香茶其實香港以前出過, 不過銷量唔好, 93-95年咁上下香港停售.<br />\n<br />\n然後唔知幾時開始, 有香港人喺澳門飲過柑香茶覺得好飲就大力吹捧, 由於香港係冇呢隻飲品關係, 柑香茶呢隻曾經喺香港黯然離場嘅飲品變成香港人喺澳門帶返香港嘅手信.<br />\n<br />\n香港陽光可能見呢隻product咁受歡迎, 兩年前喺香港重出柑香茶, 當時只有375ml包裝. 之後陽光玩懷舊包裝, 用返舊款包裝先出返250ml<br />\n<br />\n利申: 90年代嘅柑香茶FANS, 買到連士多老闆娘都認得我. 見佢重出嗰下好L開心, 不過一飲, 屌, 又甜又假. 童年回憶是美好的."},{"pid":"3fbf4f2e3603ba34cb06ac5d84809bf31ed9ef5c","tid":416080,"uid":100873,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T09:25:39.000Z","msg":"屋企做汽水飲品批發我寫單嗰陣就係唔明點解啲密瓜奶點解每次翻完貨都去得咁快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n利申:自己一次都無飲過"},{"pid":"796901f4b21754db36b1aa7004a9370934babf43","ti